### 17. `extensions/pulseboard/src/channel.test.ts`

Colocated unit tests using Vitest.

Test cases:
1. **`resolvePulseboardAccount`** — default account resolves with empty config (configured=false)
2. **`resolvePulseboardAccount`** — resolves with full config (configured=true when all three fields set)
3. **`listPulseboardAccountIds`** — returns `["default"]` for empty config
4. **`normalizePulseboardTarget`** — boards: `"#general"` → `"#general"`, `"general"` → `"general"` (DM), `""` → `null`
5. **`isBoardTarget`** — `"#foo"` = true, `"foo"` = false
6. **`pulseboardPlugin`** — has `id === "pulseboard"`, `capabilities.chatTypes` includes both `"direct"` and `"group"`, `capabilities.blockStreaming === true`
